com.intuit.ipp.services

Class BatchOperation

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intuit.ipp.services.BatchOperation

  • public class BatchOperation
extends Object
    Class to prepare the BatchItemrequets and get the responses for the corresponding bIds. The response is segregated to corresponding result types so that user can validate the corresponding batch item using the bId.
